window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The astonishing sequel to </b><b><i>Children of Time</i></b><b>, the award-winning novel of humanity's battle for survival on a terraformed planet.</b></p> <p>Thousands of years ago, Earth's terraforming program took to the stars. On the world they called Nod, scientists discovered alien life - but it was their mission to overwrite it with the memory of Earth. Then humanity's great empire fell, and the program's decisions were lost to time.</p> <p>Aeons later, humanity and its new spider allies detected fragmentary radio signals between the stars. They dispatched an exploration vessel, hoping to find cousins from old Earth.</p> <p>But those ancient terraformers woke something on Nod better left undisturbed.</p> <p>And it's been waiting for them.</p> <p>For more from Adrian Tchaikovsky, check out:<br> <i>Children of Time</i></p>"; 
